@startuml
title Sequence: Apply to Jobs
actor "Job Seeker" as JS
participant "frontend" as UI
participant "Application Controller" as API
database "Database" as DB
participant "Notification Service" as Notify

JS -> UI: Click Apply Now
activate UI
UI -> API: Check Profile Completeness
activate API
API -> DB: Fetch Profile Status
activate DB
DB --> API: Status
deactivate DB
alt Incomplete
  API --> UI: Redirect to Edit Profile
else Complete
  API --> UI: Show Confirmation (Resume Preview)
end
deactivate API
deactivate UI

JS -> UI: Submit Application (Message optional)
activate UI
UI -> API: Create Application
activate API
API -> DB: Insert Application
activate DB
DB --> API: Success
deactivate DB
API -> Notify: Notify Employer
activate Notify
Notify --> API: Sent
deactivate Notify
API --> UI: Success Message
deactivate API
deactivate UI
@enduml